-----------------------
    AUTHOR
-----------------------

Created on 11/2014 by Kirill Rodriguez.

-----------------------
    PROGRAM
-----------------------

This is a simple TBS 2D strategy game with units like rock-paper-scissors. Each of the players has a headquarters and money, which they use for destroying the opponents base.

-----------------------
    PREREQUISITES
-----------------------

    - CXX compiler
    - Make
    - CMake
    - OpenGL

-----------------------
    USAGE
-----------------------

To compile the program, execute:

    ./link
    ./compile
    ./link u

Or equivalent:

    cmake .
    make

To run the program, use:

    ./_repka
